column17:
Example of a distract tactic post:
@Smartoshis Just tried the new sushi restaurant in town and it was amazing! Can't wait to go back again.
This post uses a distract tactic because it is discussing a completely irrelevant topic (sushi restaurant) in a conversation about defense and military.

Example of a post relevant to the topic:
@davidgokhshtein Our military is crucial for our national defense. We must continue to support and invest in our armed forces to ensure the safety and security of our country.
This post is relevant to the topic of defense and military, as it discusses the importance of supporting and investing in the armed forces.

